Augustine PALMISANO and Lawrence Scrotino, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. December 17, 1929. No. 5540. Clarence J. Dowling, of New Orleans, La., for appellants. Edmond E. Talbot, U. S. Atty., and William H. Norman, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of New Orleans, La.

' Before WALKER, BRYAN, and FOSTER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
